title.rendered: Lady flex is winning against 80lb Presa Canario/Pit Bill at Tug of War!

content.rendered:
The dog wouldn’t “out” and now her owner can play tug with him and has good control of him. She lives in an apt so the controlled play and obedience helps to keep him fulfilled and happy.

My 2024 middle aged lady flex is winning against my 80lb Presa Canario/Pit Bill at Tug of War. He is upset & tired. It’s all because of the best trainer Carla at Fluent Dog Training. Early training and consistency is key.  The sweet face of defeat. He loves me and He is stronger than I. Carla taught us well.

The dog’s name is Atlas and we’ve been working together since he was a little puppy. I also trained this dog’s older sister from another litter and that’s how Atlas’ owner found me and knew I could teach her how to control a powerful dog.
